ride

Class Ride

  • java.lang.Object
    • ride.Ride

  • public class Ride
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a Ride of a Network. It has a starting and ending time, a User with its Card and a Bike. It is created without an ending time.
    Author:
    Chloé
